## 🔒 Security Flow

```
Customer → PayPal Button click
  → PayPal processes payment
  → Frontend receives { orderID } from PayPal
  → Frontend POST /api/v1/gmb-orders { paypalOrderId: orderID, ...formData }
  → Backend fetches order from PayPal API directly (server-to-server)
  → Backend verifies: status=COMPLETED AND amount >= expected SAR→USD
  → Backend saves to MongoDB as paymentStatus: 'paid'
  → Frontend shows ✅ success screen
```

